<section class="relative grit-dark section-paper">
  <div class="container relative z-10" style="padding-top: 6rem; padding-bottom: 8rem;">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-12 items-start">
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--ember-deep);">The Format</div>
        <h2 class="font-slab mt-5" style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.5rem); line-height: 0.92;">
          FOUR<br/>
          <span style="color: var(--ember-deep);">CHAIRS,</span><br/>
          ONE<br/>
          ROOM.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-6 lg:col-start-7">
        <div class="rule-ink"></div>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 leading-relaxed font-body" style="font-size: 1.0625rem; color: var(--ink-3);">
          <p class="font-serif italic leading-snug" style="font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--ink);">
            A "writers round" is a Nashville thing. Four songwriters sit in a
            circle and take turns — one plays the song, the others listen.
          </p>
          <p>
            No band, no theatrics. Each writer says where the song came from,
            then plays it the way they wrote it: voice and one acoustic
            guitar. Then the chair passes left.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our rounds bring together Christian songwriters — independent,
            signed, local, on tour — for an evening of new songs, old ones,
            and the kind of quiet conversation that only happens when the
            lights are down and the room is leaning in.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="pt-4" style="border-top: 2px solid var(--ink);">
            <div class="micro" style="color: var(--ember-deep);">EVERY</div>
            <div class="font-slab mt-2" style="font-size: 1.5rem;">2ND SAT.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-4" style="border-top: 2px solid var(--ink);">
            <div class="micro" style="color: var(--ember-deep);">DOORS</div>
            <div class="font-slab mt-2" style="font-size: 1.5rem;">5:30 PM</div>
          </div>
          <div class="pt-4" style="border-top: 2px solid var(--ink);">
            <div class="micro" style="color: var(--ember-deep);">COVER</div>
            <div class="font-slab mt-2" style="font-size: 1.5rem;">FREE</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
